                <p>
               <unclear>Ε</unclear>ἷς Θεός,<lb/>ὁ πάντων<lb/>Δεσπότη<lb break="no"/>ς. <choice>
                        <sic>Μνημῖο<lb break="no"/>ν</sic>
                        <corr>Μνημεῖον</corr>
                    </choice> Λουκίας<lb/>Πέτρου, ἁ<lb break="no"/>ποθανούσης μετὰ καλ<lb break="no"/>οῦ ὀνόματος ἐτῶν<lb/>
               <num value="20">κ</num>, τοῦ ἔτους <num value="356">τνς</num>, ἐν<lb/>μηνὶ <choice>
                        <sic>Ἀρτεμεσίου</sic>
                        <corr>Ἀρτεμισίῳ</corr>
                    </choice> ἑβδ<lb break="no"/>
               <supplied reason="omitted">ό</supplied>μῃ, ἡμέρᾳ
                    Κυρίου<lb/>ἔκτῃ. <choice>
                        <sic>Θάρ<lb break="no"/>σι</sic>
                  <corr>θάρσει</corr>
                    </choice>, Λουκία, <choice>
                        <sic>οὐδὶς</sic>
                        <corr>οὑδείς</corr>
                    </choice> ἀ<lb break="no"/>θάνα <space unit="character" quantity="1"/>
               <lb break="no"/>τος.
                        <g type="cross"/>
            </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>One (is) the God, the Lord of all. Monument of Lucia, (daughter) of Petros, who
                    died having a good name (at the age) of 20 years, in the year 356, on the
                    seventh (day) of the month Artemisios, on (the) sixth day of (the) Lord
                    (Friday). Be of good cheer, Lucia, no one is immortal.</p>
            </div>
